info.description:
Utilities for The Quantitative Criticism Lab
https://www.qcrit.org

## Installation

```bash
pip install qcrit
```

## Submission
```bash
python setup.py bdist_wheel sdist
twine upload dist/*
```

## Development
```bash
pipenv shell
pipenv install --dev
```
